seller.description: I'm Abhi, a passionate graphic designer based in India, with 7+ years of experience. I've worked with many notable clients like Nike, Cisco, EA Sports, DC Pro, Fiverr internal communications, etc. I am specialized in Logo Design and Brand Identity design. I'm available : Mon/Sat- 12am/12pm(EST). Let's connect :)

reviews.comment: The service provided was unsatisfactory. The pace of work was slower than expected, given the seller's proclaimed expertise. I had assumed more attention would be paid to moving the project forward efficiently under the seller's guidance. However, revisions took 2-3 days each, meaning I would only receive 1-2 revisions per work week, with no weekend work. This stretched the project out to a lengthy 21 days. The revisions failed to accurately implement the specific details I provided, despite the seller acknowledging my clear instructions. The end result after 21 days is a logo that feels half-finished and still needing a professional polish that I did not receive from this seller. Overall, t

Abhi was great to work with. Each day I made some revision requests I'd get up the next morning and there would be a new delivery. I felt like a kid waiting for Santa Claus!

Perhaps more importantly, Abhi came up with an imaginative and expressive design that I really feel works for my brand. I'm not artistically illiterate, despite primarily being a tech person, but I find that having good ideas on-demand, for my own purposes just creates a mental block in me. I got a good handful of suggestions right away, and while they were all great interpretations of my vague and waffley requirements, one of them really grabbed me. Two days later, it's live on YouTube. Thanks Abhi!

Creatively, very good! Abhi is wonderful! Easy to communicate with and the process went smoothly until we asked for the video source files. - We purchased the premium animated logo package which specified that it included the source files which we want so that we can continue to make changes and edits within our own team. When we arrived at the completion point of our project, we had to ask for the source files 4-5 times. We now have the files but I would advise, either don't offer the source files at all or if you do, specify the format of what you're offering (AfterEffects project file - aep) and simply say you do not take responsibility for client changes if that is the concern.

Abhi is exceptionally kind, professional in communication und fast!
He listens carefully to your needs and ideas! 
We are happy with his work. Don't expect to get what a marketing company does for thousands of bucks. You get what you pay for from a nice guy who brings in his own ideas and listens to yours. 
While his gigs say that sunday is his free day, he even took care of us on sunday without any extra costs. But please don't expect him to do so, just letting you know about his work ethics.

It was a pleasure working with Abhi. I can for the first time ever say, with all my heart, this man went above and beyond to deliver a great logo. 

It is super easy to work with Abhi, as he takes your requests seriously, and through his creativity he is able to deliver high class results. Very quick replier as well for someone across the globe.

In a sense, Abhi also wants you to have the best logo for your business, and it showed by his involvement in the project. 

I wish I could give more praise to this business, it would deserve all the merits it can get. Abhi is worth your investment.

Abhi, a very big thank you!
Thank you very much, great buyer
